>\n其實我唔明點解夾腳有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話男人都有碌棍係到夾中敏感位會爽，但係你地個粒豆咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點夾中</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n陰蒂頭只係冰山一角<br />\n外陰每個部分係夾腳時嘅拉扯<br />\n都會牽動到外陰的神經末稍產生感覺<br />\n<br />\n巴打都係了解多啲女生嘅構造先</blockquote><br />\n始終我冇塊閪，好難完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7cd30c7a62792b0402a8c89847298002d0f173c","tid":149790,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"用完手+口只會更想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97e6a8db1697b5e4992030e6a48eaf3ae03cc6a","tid":149790,"uid":3268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T12:52:31.000Z","msg":"我奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6625846c50a70a769e30f60dda2bcb6b8019c78","tid":149790,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T12:55:32.000Z","msg":"嚇死 好彩無女朋友"},{"pid":"7fd83ddfc93d5fc4073577a0d374fa6174a1dc1e","tid":149790,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"我比較喜歡男朋友個屎忽仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35d2032d09e58e18b967572322412e6a8919dda","tid":149790,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"自己都忍唔撚到啦"},{"pid":"d480084cc49c713609af0f889d216197e1fa3e47","tid":149790,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用完手+口只會更想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你自己diy個時點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f182a8400d230e8a60ceb6d9a3e4fc203475b715","tid":149790,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚇死 好彩無女朋友</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c2b8e7a0b3a2f6a56f0bc208bbbd3c0c3b077a","tid":149790,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:02:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我比較喜歡男朋友個屎忽仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁大食要屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c0af604f8b36468a680b383f8d222fac5795e1","tid":149790,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己都忍唔撚到啦</blockquote><br />\n忍唔到即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用手都照殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ab7a294e4beb65e1e1e6a08e3674f3b07c5553","tid":149790,"uid":9250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"但男人幫完女朋友奶/用手會忍到唔扯咩<br />\n聽到啲叫聲都會high啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}